Chinese Company Wins Sydney Olympics Equipment Bid
ZHENGZHOU , December 28 ( Xinhua ) -- The Zhengzhou Zhongyuan ( Central China ) Screen Technology Company Ltd. in central Henan Province won the bid to supply large color electronic scoreboards for the 27th Olympic Games which will be held in Sydney in the year 2000 .
The company outbid eight major international electronics firms , including Panasonic , Sony and Mitsubishi , in terms of technological designs , test results , technological indices and functions , according to company sources .
The company will also supply electronic advertising equipment to the city of Melbourne for the Olympic Games in the year 2000 .
